{"tid":1650404,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭提醒] 從錯誤中學習，現場定目標，唔唱肥媽，唔散播恐慌","createTime":"2019-10-13T02:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T03:11:39.000Z","uid":96148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"784202379bf45b84cdf839a0f1a2906d3339a4ca","tid":1650404,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"有好多中線朋友學緊上前d，我唔會叫你地做偽勇武，因為唔刷經驗值又點成長。但係根據呢一星期強差人意的表現，大家真係要從錯誤中學習<br />\n去現場前揾定自己嗰區有乜目標建築物，去到現場唔好等，即刻set第一第二目標，黑裝修紅裝飾，5分鐘內就要移動。<br />\n<br />\n好多時前面叫企疏d，係想有多d空間，唔係想你地走，d人愈行愈後，好容易以為大隊散緊水，所以叫你企疏d，唔該<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">企闊條路，向横發展，而唔係淨係向後退</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報哨時，唔好話邊度邊度有狗，講清楚<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有幾多，做緊咩</span></strong>，狗隻落車上gear之後，都要一段時間，接到order 之後先會咬人，唔好亂咁製造恐慌，我知有狗好得人驚，但係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每次出來都預左有狗架啦，有狗唔係縮沙唔係即刻返屋企的理由，香港人反抗，唔係嗌出來，係做出來架</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，自己温下書，邊到跌低邊度企返喺身<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZN78oca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZN78oca.jpg&h=4cb20fae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SW1Jcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SW1Jcb.jpg&h=95970142&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BR6pFYS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBR6pFYS.jpg&h=0f75b046&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HeDfNDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHeDfNDS.jpg&h=6722759b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2T5xPSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2T5xPSd.jpg&h=b834ce3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YijuSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YijuSe.jpg&h=4c8183d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c935229f55e5117ca9262869460f759f0b4ea4","tid":1650404,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc